#. Short description.
#, gp-priority: high
msgid ""
"Fast, accessible faceted product filtering for WooCommerce: AJAX filters, a "
"mobile drawer, and Core Web Vitals by design."
msgstr ""
"Szybkie, dostępne fasetowe filtrowanie produktów dla WooCommerce: filtry "
"AJAX, mobilny panel i Core Web Vitals zaprojektowane od podstaw."

#. Plugin name.
#, gp-priority: high
msgid "Sieve - Faceted Filter for WooCommerce"
msgstr "Sieve, fasetowy filtr dla WooCommerce"

#. Found in faq list item.
msgid ""
"<strong>Discussions and questions</strong> - <a "
"href=\"https://github.com/wppoland/sieve/discussions\">github.com/wppoland/sieve/discussions</a>"
